        "gg2Qn3hJVgP_text": "<p>Proven Results While You Sleep</p>",
        "gg3BajX3jAe_text": "<p>I absolutely love that <strong>refreshing</strong>, <strong>cooling feeling </strong>from a skincare product—it’s one of my favorite parts of my routine. Our mask gives you that <strong>calming, spa-like effect</strong>, even when you're just relaxing at home. It soothes, hydrates, and leaves your skin with a gorgeous, radiant glow—such a simple, <strong>luxurious way</strong> to unwind and take care of yourself! If you haven’t tried it yet, you're in for a treat!</p>",
        "gg5jhvAeOg-_text": "<p>Try It for 60 Days, Totally Risk-Free</p>",
        "gg7UbdrEDNi_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_Snapins.ai_468093164_17921313579005496_5027706299210191973_n_1080.jpg",
        "gg7UbdrEDNi_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_Snapins.ai_468093164_17921313579005496_5027706299210191973_n_1080.jpg",
        "gg7UbdrEDNi_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_Snapins.ai_468093164_17921313579005496_5027706299210191973_n_1080.jpg",
        "gg7_objrOEc_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/banner.png",
        "gg8qbjp2nD2_text": "<p>No Irritation for Sensitive Skin</p>",
        "ggFYCvYdkkz_text": "Are you finally ready to give your skin the care it deserves? 💕&nbsp;",
        "ggHIzq54zz__text": "5. Celebrity-Favorite",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_21c31ebc929e-hailey-bieber-pink-face-mask_jpg.png",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/21c31ebc929e-hailey-bieber-pink-face-mask_jpg.jpg",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_21c31ebc929e-hailey-bieber-pink-face-mask_jpg.png",
        "ggL99cbnlZo_text": "<p>GUARANTEED: In just a couple of hours, the Nifora facial mask makes your skin glow so brightly you won’t believe your mirror. If you think you've surpassed Korean beauty standards with just one application, you’re right. This is what Nifora can do for you every time you use it.</p>",
        "ggMTtLiPXuX_text": "<p>By Molly Richards<br>Last Updated September, 11 2025</p>",
        "ggN-h1PmvDV_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/For_LP_9.png",
        "ggNzvrSfCrV_text": "2. Scientifically Proven Ingredients",
        "ggOGc25WEdF_text": "<p>Here’s the exciting part—you’re in luck! We’ve got a <strong>limited-time offer</strong> just for you. I’m sure you’ll love the Bio-Collagen Mask, but if not, you will get a refund, no questions asked. It is <strong>60-day risk free</strong>, so why not give it a try? You deserve glowing skin!</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>",
        "ggOkzpODfF8_text": "6.&nbsp;Cooling &amp; Soothing Effect",
        "ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text": "<p>When I hear a product is a <strong>celebrity favorite</strong>, I have to try it—and once I tried our mask, I totally got why it’s so loved. It’s not just about the natural ingredients, but the <strong>amazing results</strong>. People are obsessed with how it gives them that <strong>flawless</strong>, <strong>youthful glow</strong>, and the best part? It’s all natural! If it’s good enough for them, it’s definitely good enough for us!</p>",
        "ggQPtwZzMvG_text": "4. Sensitive Skin Friendly",
        "ggTCZJLSmNN_text": "7. Exclusive<strong> Summer Sale</strong> is now Live!",
        "ggUMmUh3HgV_label": "<p>Shop Now</p>",
        "ggUYRw8nmHu_text": "<strong>The Korean Collagen Gel Mask 40,000+ Women Swear By</strong>",
        "ggUrpHf4v9e_text": "<p><strong>As we get older</strong>, our skin definitely needs <strong>more love</strong>. I’ve noticed my skin craves extra hydration to <strong>stay plump and glowing</strong>, and that’s where collagen comes in. Especially in its low-molecular-weight form (sounds fancy, but it works wonders!), it goes deep into your skin to <strong>keep it hydrated and refreshed all day</strong>. Trust me, it keeps my skin looking dewy and healthy, even after a long day!</p>",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0829/5330/6368/files/Kopie_van_4a84c883593649e49ddda6c20c3fe3ee_tplv-omjb5zjo8w-resize-jpeg_800_800.webp",
