        "ggvDN5djePx_text": "<p>Who says glowing skin has to be expensive? The right products can transform your skin without breaking the bank! Healthy, radiant skin doesn't have to cost a fortune!</p>",
        "ggw6GWQLv30_text": "<p>1 - 2 applications a week - instant results</p>",
